Title: Einhell 4309040 TC-SS 405E Scroll Saw 120W 240V EINTCSS405E
Description:
The Einhell TC-SS 405E 80 Watt Scroll Saw is ideal for precise, complicated work on wood, plastic, aluminium, plexi glass and gypsum. With its stable parallel arm, it is able to make easy, accurate cuts, including circles and round forms.

The scroll saw has a blower device to remove dust particles from the saw blade. The transparent saw blade protection offers optimal security, whilst still allowing excellent visibility. For mitre cuts, the work bench can be adjusted to up to 45°.

Specifications:

Input Power: 120W.
No Load Speed: 400-1,600/min.
Throat Depth: 406mm.
Max Cutting Depth: 45/90°: 20/52mm.
Table Size: 408 x 250mm, Table Tilt: 0-45°.
Weight: 12kg.
